reviews.text:
nice happy hour until 8pm- it's quite a good deal for happy hour .   you can have directly a discount offre for the drinks and free nuts. see pictures for the price.
$30- beer
$50- wine
$60- sake, spirits, cocktails 
two cocktails plus Japanese bean only cost about $80 per person. 
nice place to go before dinner !

Absolutely had the best time here. Staff and service was the best we have ever seen in HK. This was a fun atmosphere with great music. We came for drinks, but didn’t want to leave and ended up staying and trying a good portion of the menu. The food was excellent! Must try and will be back!

Went with my boyfriend and another couple. Best experience! The food was great and bellinis were delicious, but nothing beats the service. All waiters were the most attentive and kind I have ever had in Hong Kong. 100% would recommend as we will definitely be back!!!
Great atmosphere. Very accommodating to our large group.
A memorable night on Valentine's Day. Love the instant photographs.

Really cool place. Trending and modern. Urban culture. Variety. Nightlife. Bars and clubs. Beautiful people. Crazy dressed people. Everyone as he likes. I really enjoyed walking through this neighborhood and soaking up the energy. That gives impressions of which one can still feed for a long time. Very inspiring. Very recommendable.

7-11 is the landmark of Lan Kwai Fong
I saw mamy people just buy drinks there when they feel drunk a little bit just get in to the club for dance 💃🕺 tonight I get in to Graffiti club

🍷today is Saturday ladies entrance for free but man pay 100$ that 100$ will be the coupon for drink in side   only beer   choose only one drink (beer only) and they will take your coupon

They play old songs here (we will rock you,I love it,Rude.. ) i was stay there just only 20 minutes

you will have a great time if you like crowds and the night goers. you can pop into a bar or grab drinks from 7-11 and hang out in the street. be careful as the sun will be rising before you know it. 

unfortunately broke phone the night of so I lost my photos to share
Cool street lined up with bars. Not a fan of the men grabbing my friend and me to get us to go into their bars. Beware of false deals that they’ll say to get you to go inside.

Safe and fun. 
The cocktail here taste good and people do dance.
